risks[2	]{level	title	detail	mitigation}:
  medium	Agent ingestion remains manual	Pace v0 consumes structured run data but does not connect directly to an agent harness.	A strict schema plus editable TOON and JSON keeps integration boundaries explicit and testable.
  low	PDF saving depends on browser print support	Interactive PDF saving hands the document to the native print dialog.	The repository also includes a deterministic headless Chrome PDF export command.
